Usage: python pyrun.py [options]

Options:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -s *.js, --script=*.js
                        which script(s) to run
  -o OUTPUT, --output=OUTPUT
                        test results will be printed out in the given format
  --timeout=TIMEOUT     timeout limit for each test
  -n NODE, --node=NODE  couchdb ip , defaults to 127.0.0.1:5984
  -x all_docs.js,basics.js, --exclusion-filter=all_docs.js,basics.js
                        which scripts to exclude when running the tests
